    "RNNs are designed for sequential data, meaning they process time-dependent information, like:\n",
    "‚úÖ Text (NLP) ‚Äì Sentiment Analysis, Chatbots, Text Generation\n",
    "‚úÖ Speech & Audio ‚Äì Voice Assistants, Speech Recognition\n",
    "‚úÖ Time-Series Data ‚Äì Stock Price Prediction, Weather Forecasting"
