   "source": [
    "RNNs process input one step at a time, storing information in a hidden state.\n",
    "\n",
    "1Ô∏è‚É£ Takes an input (word, number, or sequence)\n",
    "2Ô∏è‚É£ Processes it while remembering past data\n",
    "3Ô∏è‚É£ Passes the hidden state to the next step\n",
    "üîπ Simple RNN Formula\n",
    "\n",
    "At each time step t:\n",
    "ht=tanh‚Å°(Wxxt+Whht‚àí1+b)\n",
    "ht‚Äã=tanh(Wx‚Äãxt‚Äã+Wh‚Äãht‚àí1‚Äã+b)\n",
    "\n",
    "Where:\n",
    "\n",
    "    xtxt‚Äã = Input at time tt\n",
    "    ht‚àí1ht‚àí1‚Äã = Previous hidden state\n",
    "    Wx,WhWx‚Äã,Wh‚Äã = Weights\n",
    "    bb = Bias\n",
    "    tanh‚Å°tanh = Activation function\n",
    "\n",
    "‚úÖ The hidden state htht‚Äã acts like memory, keeping track of past inputs."
   ]
